Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.46,0:00:06.25,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是她真正的力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:11.31,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.47,0:00:13.88,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逝去吧 到银河的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.61,0:00:19.10,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.39,0:00:22.02,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:29.78,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主炮来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.20,0:00:30.85,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:41.27,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:49.37,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会再让你们为所欲为
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.33,0:00:51.97,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌和Vajra都是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.42,0:00:55.88,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Macross Quarter
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.28,0:01:02.18,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来晚了 奥兹马
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.71,0:01:05.01,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 有点私事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:09.80,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹马少校
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.07,0:01:10.63,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.45,0:01:13.02,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我队长 SK-3
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.33,0:01:16.73,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SK-3 队长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.58,0:01:21.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.46,0:01:23.66,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为粉碎Galaxy的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.27,0:01:25.31,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为粉碎格蕾丝·奥克娜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.51,0:01:28.30,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及和她勾结的人的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.22,0:01:30.19,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Galaxy？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.72,0:01:33.82,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我们被利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.43,0:01:37.82,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他们和他们同伙的阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.64,0:01:40.73,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么根据信口雌黄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.01,0:01:44.03,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证据的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.80,0:01:46.12,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证据我有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.76,0:01:48.49,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.24,0:01:50.92,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是SK-4的识别信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.86,0:01:53.69,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.35,0:01:59.11,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看见了 他的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.81,0:02:09.61,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:11.95,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打破那障眼法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:13.09,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.34,0:02:29.09,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.77,0:02:31.30,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Battle Galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:33.39,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是被Vajra击沉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.39,0:02:37.34,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三岛总统阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:40.01,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事后详细听你解释
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.45,0:02:43.36,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括暗杀葛拉斯总统一事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:44.43,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗杀？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.54,0:02:46.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总统不是被Vajra所杀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.90,0:02:49.08,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好心理准备 雷昂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:02:58.64,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被揭穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:01.65,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些年轻人还真行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:03.32,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无伤大雅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:07.41,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在让他们做个好梦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.86,0:03:14.91,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 Battle Galaxy发射出众多热源
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:15.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.58,0:03:17.88,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ghost V9
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:19.34,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,V9？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:25.63,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:29.01,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:35.89,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SK-3向SK-4通话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.10,0:03:36.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多学长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:38.37,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到就回答
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:40.99,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢卡 葛兰上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:43.46,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来接收 阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:45.21,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.06,0:03:47.92,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:50.09,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SK-4向Battle Frontier通话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:52.29,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说 谢丽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.66,0:03:54.28,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定会救出兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.03,0:03:57.80,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 借你的力量一用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:04:01.80,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的歌 让她睁开眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.35,0:04:04.16,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:06.72,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 用你的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.73,0:04:09.37,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:13.52,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:29.95,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时 我听见了你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:33.12,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听见了你心灵的呼喊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.11,0:04:35.19,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:38.46,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无心插柳柳成荫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:42.00,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有心栽花花不开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:54.51,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随心所想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:58.52,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要 飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:07.44,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全机跟上 突击LOVE HEART
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:08.32,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:20.91,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔 赐予我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:25.55,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙 路哈尼 彼特洛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.02,0:05:28.46,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在解除你们的束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:39.55,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去曾让Macross City陷入恐惧深渊的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:41.98,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犹大系统解除
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.48,0:06:08.49,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌 听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.92,0:06:11.64,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的声音 谢丽尔的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.12,0:06:24.31,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睁开眼睛 兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.92,0:06:26.14,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.16,0:06:29.23,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找回你真正的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:36.48,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.72,0:06:46.05,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:20.69,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:22.42,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强烈的空间波
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:24.28,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以前天壤地别
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.02,0:07:32.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢丽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:36.57,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空间波急速展开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:39.59,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在逐渐构筑网络构造
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.34,0:07:43.34,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长 Vajra的行动…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:46.03,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Galaxy 到底干了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:50.09,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉到 感觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.05,0:07:52.60,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是星座
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:54.06,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是银河
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:57.67,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不再需要Little Queen
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:02.24,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们获得了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:05.29,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听令 蝼蚁们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:09.46,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在获得了整个宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:14.44,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原始文明也对这份力量惧怕 憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.77,0:08:19.75,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于进化为超时空生命体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:21.95,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借助Vajra的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:25.09,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音是格蕾丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:26.72,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大个儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.10,0:08:28.89,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.36,0:08:37.05,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无效？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:39.13,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是 次元断层？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:44.35,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对与Queen直接接通的我们来说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:45.77,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌是没有意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:47.91,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:52.36,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跪倒在我们能支配命运的神明之力下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:57.02,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 Vajra
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:09:00.17,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼睛 我的耳朵 我的手足
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.50,0:09:03.21,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着强韧的利爪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:07.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}Macross 11
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:13.00,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}行星 Eden
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:21.66,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}地球 Macross City
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:32.98,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见识我们的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.92,0:09:55.84,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:09:58.48,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌 阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.27,0:10:03.09,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢丽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:10.51,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯茜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:14.17,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.15,0:10:51.19,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:10:59.25,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:02.65,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.86,0:11:08.46,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏中弹 总算摆脱了他们的支配
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:11.58,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌唱吧 兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:16.44,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲伤愤怒与欢乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:19.55,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让所有情绪乘着歌放飞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:22.18,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:36.22,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 这次一定要阻止这场战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:39.66,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们兄妹的赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:52.20,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这首歌 兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:57.87,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的歌把Vajra…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.74,0:12:01.47,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra在兰歌的歌声影响下停止了攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:02.42,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:04.52,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是与我们为敌了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:05.60,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:09.14,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是与Vajra Queen的空间波旗鼓相当
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.17,0:12:09.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔓延开来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:20.27,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来 谢丽尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.24,0:12:23.11,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:28.20,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样 我的工作结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.67,0:12:31.16,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不剩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:33.11,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:37.39,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:45.40,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起来 谢丽尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:48.47,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谢丽尔小姐我才展翅高飞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:51.00,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为谢丽尔小姐给他力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:52.60,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多也才能飞上天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.32,0:12:54.10,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.10,0:12:56.06,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢丽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:12:57.45,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:12:59.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说过吧 绝对不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:02.98,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.53,0:13:04.41,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:06.39,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以来吧 谢丽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:09.49,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.94,0:13:11.31,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.17,0:13:13.85,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们再飞一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:15.15,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢丽尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:29.43,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.65,0:13:31.48,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:02.89,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告战场上的所有将士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:07.03,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra并非我们真正的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:12.04,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Galaxy才是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:16.54,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占据Vajra女王的格蕾丝·奥格娜等人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:18.61,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是我们真正的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:24.42,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对自己的翅膀怀有一份自豪感的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:26.46,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我们共同前行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.02,0:14:28.85,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOUND WAVE 坐标确认
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.04,0:14:32.05,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:47.85,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焦点护罩集中于主炮前端
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.59,0:14:53.33,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:05.72,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.91,0:15:07.96,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:17.91,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 无谓的挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:29.00,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直奔主岛而来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.14,0:15:29.80,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:15:58.10,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:00.19,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护了我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.83,0:16:04.72,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:07.07,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.08,0:16:09.82,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.35,0:16:11.18,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:12.50,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌声传达到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:16.12,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和谢丽尔小姐的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.30,0:16:21.69,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Varja也有自己的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:25.70,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是和我们大不相同
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:32.37,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们无法理解人类为何这么零零散散
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.62,0:16:33.89,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各做各的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.42,0:16:42.16,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以Vajra想把能用空间波交流的我\N从不明底细的人类手中救出
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:48.09,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但它们自从感知到谢丽尔小姐不同与我的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.51,0:16:50.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白我们每个人都是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:55.64,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不通过交流无法互相理解的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:57.93,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:01.11,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.82,0:17:06.82,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家拥抱吧 直到银河尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.62,0:17:20.41,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:39.28,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王的网络协议传达不到？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.90,0:17:42.61,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是歌的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:46.02,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断层护罩 再次展开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:48.35,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么才能突破
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.47,0:17:50.45,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:18:00.24,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通道 Vajra们在断层上打开了通道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.90,0:18:03.10,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全军跟上Vajra
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.11,0:18:19.34,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主炮损伤 发射不能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:22.40,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.27,0:18:40.38,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就现在 Macross Attack
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:56.85,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:16.69,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊 阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:18.50,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.62,0:19:19.96,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:24.02,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:26.35,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托付给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.91,0:19:32.77,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.16,0:19:35.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:40.42,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.75,0:19:43.86,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是人类进化的究极形态
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:45.26,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么进化
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:47.73,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿Vajra做牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.48,0:19:55.07,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.74,0:19:58.83,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我掩护你小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.18,0:19:59.92,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布瑞拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.39,0:20:01.21,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:04.38,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多 瞄准女王头部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.61,0:20:05.29,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头部？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:08.61,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra的心灵并非头部而在腹部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:11.97,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra是用肚子歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:14.79,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:17.36,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些蝼蚁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:21.19,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你们连接在一起深有体会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.83,0:20:24.48,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论到哪里人都是孤独的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:26.37,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们才…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.38,0:20:30.93,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但正因为孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:40.98,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会爱他人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.34,0:22:10.17,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.01,0:22:13.27,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是Vajra的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.62,0:22:18.03,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果Vajra是无须交流的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.48,0:22:21.50,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这首歌到底是用来做什么的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.69,0:22:23.50,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.51,0:22:25.16,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.26,0:22:29.66,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是情歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.34,0:22:31.30,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.14,0:22:33.90,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra数万年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.07,0:22:36.83,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 数亿年一次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:39.65,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与居住在其他银河的群落相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:43.31,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交配时互相呼唤的情歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.48,0:22:46.43,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱啊 爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.21,0:22:49.57,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的 亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.09,0:23:17.93,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.21,0:23:23.27,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢丽尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:35.32,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.94,0:23:52.00,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.31,0:23:55.29,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢丽尔和兰歌为我们打开的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.28,0:23:57.51,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.83,0:24:12.27,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻气全飞走了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.83,0:24:21.53,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢丽尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.57,0:24:24.21,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.56,0:24:26.38,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论歌还是恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.00,0:24:32.12,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.75,0:24:34.75,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢丽尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.47,0:24:40.18,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里开始
